WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.890 align:middle line:84%
>> On a new series,
"The Retreat,"

00:00:03.890 --> 00:00:08.189 align:middle line:84%
heading for a retreat on an
island in the North China Sea,

00:00:08.189 --> 00:00:12.170 align:middle line:84%
Nick Knowles joins a group who
are all seeking the antidote

00:00:12.170 --> 00:00:14.540 align:middle line:90%
for the strains of modern life.

00:00:14.540 --> 00:00:20.390 align:middle line:84%
This week on Gaia, on Season 2
of "Journey of Remembering"--

00:00:20.390 --> 00:00:23.300 align:middle line:84%
>> I reflect constantly
what is outside.

00:00:23.300 --> 00:00:26.300 align:middle line:84%
And it doesn't mean that
I am creating the outside.

00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:29.570 align:middle line:84%
I am just creating my
image of the outside

00:00:29.570 --> 00:00:32.259 align:middle line:90%
from my own perspective.

00:00:32.259 --> 00:00:34.780 align:middle line:10%
>> On "Journeys into the Soul"--

00:00:34.780 --> 00:00:37.030 align:middle line:10%
>> I'm not frightened anymore.

00:00:37.030 --> 00:00:40.900 align:middle line:10%
I can see my good and
bad sides, and I really

00:00:40.900 --> 00:00:42.830 align:middle line:10%
want to nurture all of them.

00:00:42.830 --> 00:00:47.290 align:middle line:10%
And the bad sides really
need my love and attention.

00:00:47.290 --> 00:00:49.810 align:middle line:10%
>> On "Stairway to the Stars"--

00:00:49.810 --> 00:00:54.190 align:middle line:10%
>> The most important key to
truly living a liberated life

00:00:54.190 --> 00:00:57.850 align:middle line:10%
in a liberated world
is freedom from within.

00:00:57.850 --> 00:01:01.690 align:middle line:10%
>> On "Dragonfly
enLightening Talks"--

00:01:01.690 --> 00:01:05.379 align:middle line:10%
>> Short-term inflammation
is protective.

00:01:05.379 --> 00:01:10.000 align:middle line:10%
It is the beginning of your
repair and your regeneration.

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:12.560 align:middle line:10%
>> On "Open Minds with
Regina Meredith"--

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:16.060 align:middle line:10%
>> It's about what's happening
in your heart and your spirit.

00:01:16.060 --> 00:01:17.860 align:middle line:10%
We've lost that connection.

00:01:17.860 --> 00:01:19.630 align:middle line:10%
Until we get that
connection back,

00:01:19.630 --> 00:01:22.120 align:middle line:10%
we're really not going
to progress much.

00:01:22.120 --> 00:01:24.490 align:middle line:84%
>> On "Beyond Belief
with George Noory"--

00:01:24.490 --> 00:01:25.640 align:middle line:90%
>> You can learn.

00:01:25.640 --> 00:01:29.490 align:middle line:84%
You can grow through
either chaos or harmony.

00:01:29.490 --> 00:01:32.680 align:middle line:90%
They're both available to us.

00:01:32.680 --> 00:01:35.550 align:middle line:90%
>> Only on Gaia.

00:01:35.550 --> 00:01:38.000 align:middle line:90%